  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">In the <span class=\"italic \">xy</span>-plane, the graph of <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"y equals, x plus 3 \"></span></span> intersects the graph of <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"y equals, 2 x minus 6\"></span></span> at the point <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"with coordinates a, comma b\"></span></span>. What is the value of <span class=\"italic\">a</span> ?</p>\n",
